race.description: Natalie Sax @ Belle Of The Turf 28th Dec Handicap
race.comment: DETENDU (1) finds an easier contest today and is set to peak third-up. No match for the handy Mailata when third over 1000m at this course. Didn't get a clear crack at them in the straight last time and no excuses today. SUNDAY TYCOON (6) struggled to run the 1200m out on the soft going when eighth at this track. Regular rider hops back on from the good draw. A repeat of his second to Crepe Myrtle two-back keeps him in the contest. STORMFIELD (7) lightly raced gelding resuming. Has scored two slick trial wins and is expected to go on with the job this preparation. OCEANS ONE (2) no match for the speedy Bremel at latest when a fighting third over 1000m at Wyong. That form has since been franked with Bremel winning at Canterbury last Friday night. Respect.
